{"tid":624931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收費版facebook唔會有廣告，會收幾多錢呢？？","createTime":"2018-04-11T04:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T07:00:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b03b8eb66a07db2c750b9f61ddde2cc31050eb2","tid":624931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/124651_658afd0e92074cbbc5b6c3a5d3333b58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F124651_658afd0e92074cbbc5b6c3a5d3333b58.png&h=b14bd0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱克伯格暗示Facebook可能推出收費版本？<br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n社交媒體Facebook創辦人朱克伯格周二出席聽證會，其言論暗示Facebook不排除推出其他版本，可能包括收費版或高端版。 <br />\n<br />\n被參議院議員問及Facebook會否永久免費時，朱克伯格回答指：「對，這以後都會有一個版本的Facebook是免費的。」他並認為，由廣告支持的服務對Facebook來說是最好的商業模式。 <br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格指，「Facebook的使命是協助全球各地的人聯繫在一起，令世界變得更緊密，因此我們有必要提供所有人都負擔得起的服務。」 <br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，朱克伯格特別提到會有「一個版本」的Facebook是免費，而不是Facebook網站一向承諾的「永久免費」。 <br />\n<br />\n這意味着，該公司不排除推出一個收費版本的Facebook，或許是「零廣告」的版本，而此舉將有助Facebook緩和用戶對於資料外洩的憂慮。 <br />\n<br />\nFacebook股價周二大幅反彈，收報165.04美元，升4.5%。 <br />\n─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─"},{"pid":"eeffd95a504ed2f18a302ea523eec17e809df980","tid":624931,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"學到嘢喎豬仔<br />\n啲語言藝術好中國風下喎"},{"pid":"fa031df34ee9b58eadac3c506295febea1753b30","tid":624931,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"畀唔畀錢都係睇content farm<br />\n只係唔畀錢就要睇埋scam廣告<br />\n有個閪分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf233cb5bafb46b5854b9141d92ee44e633e8b6d","tid":624931,"uid":21355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"fb老嘢先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2049e28999d0a98a82662f22e12b68edf0967f","tid":624931,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d942d1038e7417ff1b12cbbb5fafbba59ed604","tid":624931,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"發揮連仔力量 憾低Facebook <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}